name: 2006-Nen 10-Gatsu Taikenban Soft
overview: This is a demo compilation cartridge which was used in Japanese store kiosks. It contains a total of five games, which include: - Adult full-time training DS - Custom Robo Rumble - Kirby Squeak Squad - New Super Mario Bros DS - Tetris DS. Many features that appear within the retail game are locked from being used by the player.
